Encounter.Name: Cloud City Grand Prix
Encounter.Notes:
This encounter contains the three rival racing teams for the Grand Prix. Feel free to upgrade any of the cloud cars to give the PCs a run for their money.[P]
It also contains an example Velkor for Buoy Seven to Eight. The Velkor is a combination of a vehicle profile, plus an adversary. It is actually one creature; do not use the wound and soak for the adversary, use only the hull and defenses for the vehicle. If the "vehicle" is destroyed, the creature is defeated.

CharVehicle.Notes: This vehicle is driven by the Stormhawks corporate team
This vehicle is driven by the Hutt Cartel team
This vehicle is driven by Tarryn Rayzer.
